Blurb::
Choose the sampler for Markov Chain Monte Carlo
Description::
The specification of the algorithm which governs the Markov Chain Monte Carlo (MCMC) algorithm used. There currently are two options for metropolis: 
\li the option \c hastings specifies a standard Metropolis-Hastings algorithm
\li the option \c adaptive specifies the adaptive Metropolis in which the covariance of the proposal density is updated adaptively.
